qas.question: What is the average annual snowfall in Tibet?
What weather pattern exerts some influence on eastern TIbet?
What are winters like in Tibet?
What has an annual average of only 9 inches?

plausible_answers.text: The atmosphere is severely dry nine months of the year, and average annual snowfall is only 18 inches

qas.question: What effect does the shadow rain have on Tibet?
What influences the weather in northern Tibet?
